# Navigation user feedback

When the user shares **audio transcript**, **dictated notes**, or **screenshots** about navigating the deployed app (Vercel / Panelin / Calculadora) and wants a **structured report** for implementation agents:

1. Read and follow: `.cursor/skills/navigation-user-feedback/SKILL.md`
2. Output: `docs/team/ux-feedback/USER-NAV-REPORT-YYYY-MM-DD.md` using `docs/team/ux-feedback/TEMPLATE-USER-NAV-REPORT.md` as structure.
3. Do not invent UI not shown in attachments or text; use `NEEDS_CONFIRMATION` when evidence is missing.

## Triggers

- Transcripción, notas de voz en texto, feedback de navegación
- Capturas de pantalla + comentarios de uso
- "Informe de usuario", "reporte de navegación", "incorporar feedback al proyecto"
- skill name: `navigation-user-feedback`

